  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんにでもやる気を見せて
もっと積極的に行動してくれ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You should be enthusiatic about everything
you do, and be more proactive in what you do.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>熱い気持ちを忘れずにね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't forget your feelings of passion.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ま、そういうこったな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that's his spiel.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そのわりにはあんたの相方
あんまやる気あるように見えねぇけどな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Despite that though, your partner
doesn't look all that enthusiastic.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね。
燃える心とかなさそう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's true. Doesn't look like he
has much of a passionate heart.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ確かにねぇな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, that's pretty much true.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ……いい加減にしてくれ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri... Knock it off already...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
